steps.name: Step 10 : Click on Material master from left side menus
Step 11 : Click on view dropdown icon
Step 12 : Click on Default view option
Step 13 : Click on add new record button
Step 14 : Click on Sequential Material option
Step 16 : Get Material type from Excel: FERT
Step 17 : Click on Industry sector field
Step 18 : Get Industry sector from Excel: Mechanical engineering
Step 19 : Enter value in Material description field
Step 20 : Get Material description from Excel: AUTO TEST
Step 21 : Click on Plant Data - add... button
Step 22 : Get Plant Data from Excel: PLANT 0001
Step 25 : Click on Sales Data - add... button
Step 26 : Get Sales Data from Excel: Sales org. 001
Step 29 : Select value from X-Plant Material Status field
Step 31 : Click on Add row button in Language grid section
Step 33 : Select German language from option
Step 35 : Click on save on form view
Step 36 : No need to enter Manufacturer Part Number
Step 40 : Message display:  Record creation request saved successfully
Step 42 : Refreshing page for visible latest created record
Step 44 : Click on Material master from left side menus
Step 46 : Click on view dropdown icon
Step 47 : Click on Default view option
Step 48 : Click on first value action icon
Step 49 : Select view process log option
Step 50 : Blank page appear in view process log popup
Step 51 : Close the process log popup
Step 54 : --- User login as reviewer credentials
